# Large design binaries — kept locally, deliberately not versioned.
# Untitled.fig is ~43MB and Dark Landing.png ~7MB; git history is permanent, so
# committing them would bloat every future clone. The design source of truth is
# the Claude Design project (see DECISIONS.md F2), and the exported .dc.html
# files in design-reference/ are versioned instead — those are what the CSS was
# ported from. Dark Landing.png is additionally a *stale* export and must not be
# treated as a reference.
# If these ever need versioning, use Git LFS rather than committing directly.
Untitled.fig
Dark Landing.png
